Question.Context: The T-TENG was characterized for its performance under different conditions. The output power density and voltage were measured to assess its energy harvesting capability.
Question.Question: What was the output power density of the T-TENG with an external load resistance of 10^10 Ω?
Question.Source: The power density of T-TENG was ~ 0.03 W/m2 with an external load resistance of 10^10 Ω.
